# TanStack AI (useChat + fetchHttpStream)

- Chat UI uses `useChat` from `@tanstack/ai-react` with a **connection** built from `fetchHttpStream` (from `@tanstack/ai-client`).
- Backend must return **NDJSON** (newline-delimited JSON) in the **AG-UI protocol**: `RUN_STARTED`, `TEXT_MESSAGE_START`, `TEXT_MESSAGE_CONTENT`, `TEXT_MESSAGE_END`, `RUN_FINISHED`, or `RUN_ERROR`. Each line is one JSON object.
- Use `credentials: 'include'` and appropriate headers (`Accept: application/x-ndjson`, `Content-Type: application/json`) when calling `/api/chat`.
- See `docs/developer/frontend/ai-chat.md` and `docs/developer/backend/ai-chat.md`.
